{"word":"εὐκλεής","slug":"εὐκλεής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>εὐκλεής</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κλέος'><el>κλέος</el></a>\n<p/><i>of good report, famous, glorious</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>εὐκλεέστατος βίος</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b> <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-εῶς</el>, epic <el>-ειῶς</el>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; <el>κατθανεῖν</el> <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>; <a href='S:Superlative'>Sup.</a> <el>εὐκλεέστατα</el>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/>"}]}